# CODEOWNERS — review ownership for the AIRES monorepo (ADR 0017).
#
# GitHub matches the LAST matching rule per file. Order is therefore important:
# the default `*` rule comes first, then the protected paths override it.
#
# TODO: replace the placeholder handles below with real GitHub teams in the
# owning org before enabling branch protection. They are intentionally NOT a
# personal account — CODEOWNERS pointing at one person makes that person a
# single point of failure for every review.

# Default owner for everything not matched by a more specific rule below.
*                       @your-org/software-factory

# --- Model 1 protected paths (ADR 0017 "Keeping the Intake app stable") ---
# The Intake app must stay very stable, and @sf/shared is a load-bearing
# contract that ripples into BOTH apps at build time. No change reaches these
# paths without the owner's approval.
/apps/intake/           @your-org/intake-owners
/packages/shared/       @your-org/intake-owners
